I do get tears slightly.

102
00:07:57,643 --> 00:08:01,414
Well, it's our own song
and it's a song written by our member.

103
00:08:01,481 --> 00:08:03,649
Right, it's a special song.

104
00:08:03,716 --> 00:08:06,652
So, you know, it speaks for us.

