00:08:58,938 --> 00:09:04,477
{\an8}WHEN I LOOK OVER, YOU'RE WITH ME

122
00:09:04,911 --> 00:09:06,779
<i>In "Time View,"</i>

123
00:09:06,846 --> 00:09:10,516
<i>that line that says,
"When I look over, you're with me."</i>

124
00:09:10,583 --> 00:09:12,785
I do look over, yes.

125
00:09:12,852 --> 00:09:14,487
I'm singing, "When I look over,"

126
