131
00:09:30,970 --> 00:09:33,072
I don't want them to glare at me,

132
00:09:33,139 --> 00:09:35,207
but I want them to glance this way.

133
00:09:35,274 --> 00:09:38,411
If they do, I'll probably get goosebumps.

134
00:09:39,245 --> 00:09:41,881
I'm gonna state it here,
everyone's review.

135
00:09:42,582 --> 00:09:45,151
